OL,3,CDisabled woman stuck in flat for
OL,4,Calmost three weeks due to broken lift
OL,6,FA disabled woman from Reading says
OL,7,Fshe's been stuck in her flat for
OL,8,Falmost three weeks after the lift in
OL,9,Fher block broke.
OL,11,F60-year-old Julie Maskell has Multiple
OL,12,FSclerosis and lives on the third floor
OL,13,Fof Belford Court in Laud Close.
OL,15,FThe building's only lift broke down on
OL,16,FJanuary 19th 2024.
OL,18,FThe housing association, Housing
OL,19,FSolutions, says it's trying to source
OL,20,Fa part needed to repair the lift and
OL,21,Fhas apologised to residents.
