OL,6,FJulie's father, Mike Shaw, told ITV
OL,7,FNews Meridian that his daughter is
OL,8,Fbecoming increasingly anxious.
OL,10,FThe 86-year-old said: "Three weeks
OL,11,Fago, she rang us and said she wouldn't
OL,12,Fbe able to come over for her weekly
OL,13,Fvisit as the lift was out of action.
OL,15,F"My wife and I are in our eighties and
OL,16,Fwe are not mobile enough to climb six
OL,17,Fflights of stairs to see her.
OL,19,F"She is just stuck up there."
