OL,6,FIt's Julie's birthday on February 14th
OL,7,Fbut it's not known if the life will be
OL,8,Ffixed by then.
OL,10,FThe 60-year-old said: "I need to see
OL,11,Fmy parents. It's getting to me now. I
OL,12,Fjust miss them.
OL,14,F"I try not to think about it because
OL,15,Fit's the only way I can deal with it.
OL,16,FWhen I do think about it, I can't
OL,17,Fbreathe as you think there's no way
OL,18,Fout."
