OL,6,FA spokesperson for Housing Solutions
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are so sorry for the
OL,8,Fcontinued disruption to residents
OL,9,Fliving at Belford Court brought about
OL,10,Fby the lift not working for a
OL,11,Fprolonged period.
OL,13,F"We are working hard with our
OL,14,Fspecialist lift contractor to source a
OL,15,Freplacement part needed to repair the
OL,16,Flift as a matter of urgency, to get
OL,17,Fthe lift back into operation as soon
OL,18,Fas possible.
