OL,6,F"Housing Solutions staff are talking
OL,7,Fto residents regularly and we have
OL,8,Foffered additional support that each
OL,9,Fperson might need. Where a resident
OL,10,Fhas taken up the support we have
OL,11,Foffered or asked for additional help,
OL,12,Fthis has been provided.
OL,14,F"We understand completely how
OL,15,Ffrustrating this situation is for our
OL,16,Fresidents and we want to thank them
OL,17,Ffor their patience and understanding
OL,18,Fwhile we resolve the lift issue."
